Giorgi Margvelashvili Giorgi Margvelashvili Kari Georgia: , kngkawas 1969 idas 9 diyax 4 ), Georgia Pingruncya, Seyjicya. Kngkawas 2013 dhuq kngkawas 2018 ngalan Soto Georgia.
